title: Sutton keeper Wayne Shaw chomps a pie gives two fingers up to the modern footballer’s lean diet
text:
EFL He Shaw is hungry Sutton keeper Wayne Shaw chomps a pie gives two fingers up to the modern footballer’s lean diet 
Back-up United stopper was snapped munching down on the baked goods on the touchline after bookies had given odds of 8-1 on him doing exactly that Pictured
